<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa lungkhamna kalvari lam chu zuonin,
 Thagau thiengtho, aw ei pui zelin;
 Muh ka nuom ie ei hukdampa chu.
 A linglukhuk leh a thawkna chu

[V2]
 A na na lawm lawm e, ei tatna;
 A khut, a keng a nak ah aliem ma-ha a thuok;
 Kei di'n kraws chungah a hin a piei.

[V3]
 2. Nicheng in ka ngaihtuoh Hukdampa thihna mun chu
 Ginnan khawvel apat hin ka mui;
 Migilote kal ah a khai ui.
 Siktui ngaiin sunnau bang a mau.

[V4]
 3. Ngai un, Hukdampa lungngai leh thavai in a mau
 &quot;Ka Pathien bang dinga ei taihsan,?
 A paucham Amah khenden te di'n,
 Kraws chunga a thih ding kuon khan le.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa, amau dinga Na thawkna kalvari ah.
 Mitin pui inla ki-etsakin;
 He leu amau dinga Na thawkna.
 Lal Isu hun pak lo thei puon au.</lyrics>
<title>Lungkhamna Kalvari</title>
<hymn_number>52</hymn_number>
<author>Thanhera</author>
</song>